4.00	Paul_Ortiz	Paul Ortiz	Paul Antonio Ortiz is a guitarist and musician from Colchester, UK. He is most famous for his work under his solo project name of Chimp Spanner. Both his 2004 album Imperium Vorago and his 2009 album At The Dream's Edge are entirely self produced in Ortiz' home studio. Ortiz also composes for computer games, advertising, television and radio, and his clients range from Red Bull to Dolby Laboratories.	
